---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroImage from "@/images/navic_top.avif";
import buildingImage from "@/images/building.avif";
---

<section class="space-y-16 md:space-y-24">

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl my-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 md:overflow-visible">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12 md:overflow-visible">

      <div class="flex-1 relative z-10 md:pt-16 lg:pt-24 md:overflow-visible md:min-w-0">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-sky-900 leading-tight md:whitespace-nowrap md:pr-8">
          人とのつながりを大切に。<br />
          様々な分野で新たな価値を生み出していく。
        </h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex-1 relative w-full md:w-auto md:mt-16 lg:mt-24 md:z-0 md:flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="relative">
          <Image 
            src={heroImage} 
            alt="hero image" 
            width={800} 
            height={600}
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">

      <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-auto">
        <Image 
          src={buildingImage} 
          alt="building image" 
          width={800} 
          height={600}
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-sky-800 leading-tight">
          常に先を見据えた<br />
          事業展開で<br />
          新たな未来を切り開く。
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
